    <Solution>Align HL naming with LL by renaming HL-MAP-2.2 to "Cell Classification" and propagate this corrected term to LL references (e.g., LL-MAP-2.2). Validate traceability mappings from HL to LL after the change.</Solution>
  </Finding>
</Findings>
